[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0347","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0174","title":"SGI Skunkware 2.0 view-source CGI 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Skunkware 2.0 的 view-source CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感信息泄露，影响 Skunkware 2.0 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0174"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.550","remediation":"立即停止并移除 /cgi-bin/view-source CGI 脚本；如业务需要该功能，重写脚本并对路径参数做严格的输入过滤，拒绝包含 \"../\"、绝对路径或特殊字符的请求；同时在 Web 服务器层面（Apache/Nginx）配置 `AllowOverride None` 和 `Options -Indexes`，并添加访问控制规则阻止对 CGI 目录的未授权访问。由于 Skunkware 2.0 已停止维护多年，建议迁移至较新的操作系统发行版及标准 Web 服务器软件包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0174","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20568","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0174","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0174.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0174.md","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j/GHSA-mfjc-659f-pj9j.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0347.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0129","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0047","title":"Sendmail MIME转换缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"sendmail 8.8.3 及 8.8.4 版本在处理 MIME 邮件编码转换时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标邮件服务器发送特制的 MIME 邮件触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，可能造成服务崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 sendmail 邮件传输代理，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0047"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.130","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.8.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 MIME 转换中的缓冲区溢出问题。若无法立即升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中禁用 MIME 转换功能（O MimeVersion=0）或限制邮件大小作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/685"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0129.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0130","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0048","title":"Unix Talkd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Talk 服务守护进程（talkd）在处理 DNS 响应信息时存在输入验证缺陷，当攻击者向目标系统提供特制的恶意 DNS 数据时，可导致缓冲区溢出或命令注入，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多种 UNIX 变种系统（包括 AIX、HP-UX、Solaris 等），攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0048"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.283","remediation":"建议立即禁用 talkd 服务（在 inetd.conf 或 xinetd.d 中注释掉 talk 条目并重启服务），如必须使用应升级至修复该漏洞的版本。同时在边界防火墙上屏蔽 UDP 端口 517（talkd 默认端口），限制对 talk 服务的网络访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/147"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0130.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0194","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0081","title":"wu-ftpd RNFR 命令文件覆盖漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd FTP 服务器在实现 FTP 重命名功能时存在路径验证缺陷，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过 FTP 协议发送特制的 RNFR（重命名来源）与 RNTO（重命名为）命令序列，将服务器上的任意文件重写为指定目标文件名，导致文件被覆盖或篡改。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd FTP 服务器，攻击者无需登录认证即可利用匿名 FTP 会话执行操作，成功利用可覆盖系统配置文件或可执行文件，进而可能导致服务异常中断或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0081"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1997-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.170","remediation":"wu-ftpd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 或 Pure-FTPd 等活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件。迁移前，在 /etc/hosts.allow 和防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务仅对可信 IP 段开放，并禁用匿名用户写入权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0081","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0081"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0194.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0131","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0049","title":"SGI IRIX Csetup 任意文件创建或覆盖漏洞","description":"IRIX 操作系统中的 Csetup 工具存在任意文件创建或覆写漏洞，由于未对用户输入的文件路径进行充分校验，具有本地访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞创建或覆盖系统关键文件，从而提升权限或导致系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0049"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.417","remediation":"将 IRIX 升级至 6.3 或更高版本；若无法升级，立即移除 Csetup 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/Csetup），并限制不可信用户的本地登录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0049"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0131.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0136","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0051","title":"SGI IRIX FLEXlm LicenseManager 任意文件创建与远程代码执行漏洞","description":"FLEXlm LicenseManager（lmgrd）许可管理守护进程 4.0 至 5.0 版本存在文件创建与程序执行漏洞。该漏洞源于 FLEXlm 对用户提交的请求未进行充分校验，导致本地攻击者可利用 lmgrd 进程的权限创建任意文件或执行恶意程序，进而获取目标系统的完全控制权。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 及 Sun Solaris 等多个 Unix 平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此问题，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0051"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.673","remediation":"升级 FLEXlm License Manager 至 5.0 以上版本，或禁用 License Manager 服务。在无法升级的环境下，通过防火墙限制对 lmgrd 端口 (TCP/UDP 27000-27009) 的访问，仅允许受信客户端连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0051","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19350","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8/GHSA-68w9-8p8f-9gr8.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0136.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0136.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0849","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0582","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 账户锁定策略安全配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统的账户锁定策略存在安全配置缺陷，默认或不当的锁定阈值、锁定持续时间和重置时间设置使得攻击者可对用户账户实施暴力破解攻击。由于缺乏足够的登录失败锁定保护，远程攻击者能够通过自动化工具反复尝试密码，直至获得有效凭证，进而获取系统未授权访问权限，影响系统机密性和完整性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0582"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.593","remediation":"在 Windows NT/2000 的本地安全策略中，将\"账户锁定阈值\"设为 5 次无效登录，\"账户锁定时间\"设为 30 分钟，\"重置账户锁定计数器\"设为 30 分钟。通过「管理工具→本地安全策略→账户策略→账户锁定策略」进行配置，或使用组策略进行域范围下发。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0582","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0582.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0582.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000134.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0849.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0841","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0841.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0576","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全关键文件审核日志缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的文件审核策略存在缺陷，系统未对安全关键文件或目录的访问事件记录成功或失败审核日志，导致攻击者可在不被记录的情况下访问敏感文件。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。利用方式为直接访问未受日志监控的敏感文件，在无审核记录的情况下窃取凭据或系统配置等关键数据，安全审计机制失效且无法追溯攻击行为。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0576"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.873","remediation":"通过\"域用户管理器\"→\"策略\"→\"审核\"，启用\"审核文件及对象访问\"的成功和失败审核。在资源管理器中右键关键文件/目录→\"属性\"→\"安全性\"→\"审核\"，配置具体的 SACL 条目审计敏感访问操作。使用 Security Configuration Manager (SCM) 定义审核策略模板并批量应用到域内所有 Windows NT 系统，确保安全关键路径的访问日志完整记录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0576","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0576","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0576.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3gh3-crhx-q3jq/GHSA-3gh3-crhx-q3jq.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e2f73fd4-247a-4b46-b8bb-c1a20c030c99.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0841.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0840","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0575","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全审核策略事件日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的用户审核策略存在安全配置缺陷，导致登录/注销、文件和对象访问、用户权限使用、用户和组管理、安全策略更改、系统重启/关机及进程跟踪等关键安全事件无法正确记录成功或失败日志。远程攻击者可在未触发审计日志的情况下进行未授权访问和权限提升操作，严重降低了系统的事后追溯和取证分析能力，影响 Windows NT 全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0575"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.760","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中通过「域用户管理器」→「规则」→「审核」启用所需审核策略（至少启用登录/注销、文件及对象访问、用户权限使用、用户及组管理、安全策略更改、重启/关机/系统事件、进程追踪等类别的事件成功与失败审核）。另可通过注册表路径 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SECURITY\\Audit 修改策略键值强制启用完整审核日志。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统并启用安全审核策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000132.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0838","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0572","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 注册表编辑器 .reg 文件关联漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，.reg 文件默认关联至注册表编辑器 (regedit)，攻击者可利用电子邮件附件或网页下载等方式诱骗用户打开恶意 .reg 文件，无需人工确认即可自动导入并修改注册表项，导致系统安全配置被篡改、恶意软件获得自启动权限或关键服务被禁用。该攻击无需任何身份验证，利用门槛极低，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0572"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.637","remediation":"建议将 Windows NT 4.0 升级至 Windows 2000 及以上受支持版本，或在注册表编辑器中将 .reg 文件的默认打开方式从 regedit 改为记事本，同时在组策略中禁止非管理员用户通过注册表脚本导入功能导入 .reg 文件，并加强用户安全意识培训，不双击打开来源不明的 .reg 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/178","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0572","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0572.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86060/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000131.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0825","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0562","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 空会话远程注册表访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 存在空会话（Null Session）远程访问注册表的权限漏洞。未经身份认证的攻击者可通过 SMB 协议建立空会话连接，远程匿名访问目标系统的注册表，获取系统配置、用户账户信息、网络共享设置等敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有 SP 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Microsoft 至今未完全移除该默认行为，需通过修改注册表或限制 IPC$ 访问进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0562"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.693","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a，并设置注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\LSA 下的 RestrictAnonymous 值为 2，禁止空会话枚举 SAM 账号和共享。同时禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP，在防火墙层面阻止 137-139、445 端口的外部入站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19372","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0562","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0562.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/c359f282ec6bc3eb6912ee4649970789e923d257/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m/GHSA-6wh7-hrcm-fv9m.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_registry_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0814","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0550","title":"路由器路由表远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"部分路由器设备配置不当或存在权限校验缺陷，导致任意远程主机无需认证即可通过特定协议查询并获取路由器的完整路由表信息。攻击者可借此掌握目标网络的拓扑结构、子网划分及可达路径，为后续针对性网络攻击（如中间人攻击、路由劫持）提供侦察基础。该漏洞危害等级高，影响多种主流路由器设备，CVSS 评分 7.5。建议限制 SNMP 等管理协议的访问来源，配置 ACL 规则以限制路由信息查询权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0550"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.973","remediation":"在路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），仅允许信任的管理网段访问 SNMP、Telnet/SSH 及 Web 管理端口；关闭未使用的 SNMP 服务或将 SNMP 字符串设为只读并改用复杂 community 字符串；禁用路由协议的明文邻居通告（如 Cisco 路由器使用 `no ip route-cache same-interface` 配合 `distribute-list` 过滤路由表查询）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0550"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0803","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0535","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 密码策略配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统的账户密码策略存在安全配置不当缺陷，密码长度、密码最长使用期限及密码唯一性等关键安全参数未合理设置。攻击者可利用弱密码策略通过暴力破解或字典攻击手段获取合法用户账户权限，从而实现对目标系统的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000，系统管理员需手动修正密码策略配置以消除风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0535"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.003","remediation":"通过「管理工具→本地安全策略→账户策略→密码策略」配置：密码长度最小值≥8个字符、密码最长使用期限≤90天、强制密码历史≥5个（防止重复使用最近密码）、密码必须符合复杂性要求（启用）。在域环境中通过组策略统一部署。同时禁用空白密码。该配置适用于 Windows NT 4.0/2000/XP 及后续版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0802","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0534","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 用户权限不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT/2000 存在用户权限分配不当的安全漏洞，系统管理员可能为普通用户授予了过高的系统权限，包括作为操作系统的一部分、添加工作站、备份文件和目录、更改系统时间、创建页面文件、调试程序、生成安全审计、增加配额、加载卸载设备驱动程序、锁定内存页、获取文件或其他对象的所有权等特权。本地用户可利用获得的过高权限绕过安全限制，执行未经授权的系统操作，进而影响系统完整性和机密性。此漏洞源于 Windows NT/2000 权限模型中对用户权限的细粒度控制不足，攻击者需具有本地访问权限才能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0534"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.877","remediation":"审核并移除不必要的用户权限分配，打开「管理工具 → 本地安全策略 → 用户权限指派」，逐项检查「作为操作系统的一部分」「调试程序」「取得文件或其他对象的所有权」等权限，仅分配给 Administrators 组。由于 Windows NT/2000 已停止支持，强烈建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+，并在升级前通过组策略限制用户权限遵循最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0534"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0782","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0525","title":"多种厂商 IP 协议 Traceroute 路由跟踪信息泄露漏洞","description":"IP 路由跟踪功能默认允许来自任意主机的探测请求，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过发送 TTL 递增的 ICMP 或 UDP 数据包逐跳探测目标网络的路由路径，从而获取网络拓扑结构、内部 IP 地址段及中间网关信息。此类信息泄露可为后续定向攻击提供侦察支撑，扩大攻击面。建议在网络边界配置防火墙规则限制 ICMP 时间超时响应，或禁用不必要的路由跟踪响应来缓解该风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0525"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.923","remediation":"在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），过滤入站 ICMP Time Exceeded 报文（ICMP type 11），或直接禁用从外网发起的 traceroute 请求（UDP 端口 33434-33534、ICMP Echo 及 TCP 高端口探测）。在 Linux 系统可设置 `sysctl -w net.ipv4.icmp_ignore_bogus_error_responses=1` 降低信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0525"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml"}]